	- No functional changes.

	- [dist] Move spec prereqs from RuntimeRequires to
	  DevelopRecommends to reduce deps but still allow indicating spec
	  requirement.


0.05    2015-07-30 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- Mention App::PericmdUtils.


0.04    2015-05-23 (PERLANCAR)

	- wrap-with-perinci-sub-wrapper: Add options --core, --core-or-pp,
	  --pp.


0.03    2015-05-13 (PERLANCAR)

	- [Bugfix] Forgot to set code from cmdline argument.


0.02    2015-05-13 (PERLANCAR)

        - Add utility: wrap-with-perinci-sub-wrapper.


0.01    2015-04-12 (PERLANCAR)

        - First release, contains CLI scripts split from some other
          distributions to reduce dependencies on those dists.
